snippet.title: Orderly Havoc Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist Orderly Havoc here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2363310/Orderly_Havoc/

Orderly Havoc is a time management game where you must do chores. Each chore has a unique minigame requiring timing or solving. Do this before you stress out or else you'll have a panic attack.
